headline: Senate Weighs Effectively Killing Rule That Drove Rise of Fuel-Efficient Cars
summary: Automakers are split over a measure to eliminate fines for failing to meet mileage standards that helped launch fuel-efficient mainstays like Toyota’s Prius.
